{"tid":450187,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［？？？］厭倦與外星人戰鬥　美國漢4千萬港元賣牧場","createTime":"2017-10-28T02:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T03:04:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b13976df977b4abb0731f6091c6aba2b5c58a7d2","tid":450187,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/103807_75f8d1b34e8bd0304ae3e9446c54fa8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F103807_75f8d1b34e8bd0304ae3e9446c54fa8e.jpg&h=2b665e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國亞利桑那州一個佔地4萬平方米牧場，有泳池、有牧草倉。惟牧場主人艾德蒙茲（John Edmonds）卻索價500萬美元（約3900萬港元），要將牧場賣走，到底有甚麼原因？原來牧場的後花園，竟然有一個可以讓外星人到來的「門口」。艾德蒙茲表示，厭倦了每日要與外星人戰鬥的日子，所以要將牧場出售。<br />\n<br />\n艾德蒙茲表示，自己自20年前搬到位於彩虹谷（Rainbow Valley）的「星塵」（Star Dust）牧場當天開始，就已經有奇怪的體驗。他指外星人綁架了他去進行醫學實驗，更傷害他的太太和牧場中的動物。他補充，外星人有一次將他的太太升起至半空，將她由主人房帶到室外泊車的位置，企圖綁架她到太空船。<br />\n<br />\n艾德蒙茲更將一些自稱與外星人戰鬥造成的傷口和疤痕上傳至Facebook，寫道：「這就是我想走的原因」；他形容那些是他與外星人「大打出手」的戰績。而在他上載的照片中，有一張顯示一把刀和一大灘紅色液體。艾德蒙茲聲稱，他用武士刀砍傷了外星人但它逃走了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/103822_f7000a358c24376b7c37dbdea51ee021.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F103822_f7000a358c24376b7c37dbdea51ee021.jpg&h=30714a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/103823_39883e01c5b643179d362c637b5e7b24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F103823_39883e01c5b643179d362c637b5e7b24.jpg&h=168a187b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171027/mobile/bknint-20171027192304671-1027_17011_001.html#popupGallery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171027%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20171027192304671-1027_17011_001.html%23popupGallery&d=pphi4WxfPFt3MC%2BZqVzhVhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=3df504fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171027/mobile/bknint-20171027192304671-1027_17011_001.html#popupGallery</a>"},{"pid":"7634b8c2b0a61a4958b8b5b00858b080243ffc5b","tid":450187,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:45:07.000Z","msg":"精神病?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9700f5dbb188f590ea0c0e13492d952d0c511def","tid":450187,"uid":16902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c85f1551bcb46dde17a2ecee3924716133bc01d","tid":450187,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>精神病?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n癡線佬黎講佢都幾有米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40ad261bd590dfe3c72966562427c66db6329ef","tid":450187,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"有血既拎去驗下咪知"},{"pid":"511047954683b41ba63ded1c6684dccf96dcb8a1","tid":450187,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"正啊"},{"pid":"6a072f8645673b901c497cb6fcb5af3d97d04a33","tid":450187,"uid":47160,"like":0,"di